            <title>[SPARK-18342] HDFSBackedStateStore can fail to rename files causing snapshotting and recovery to fail</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/SPARK-18342</link>
                <project id="12315420" key="SPARK">Spark</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The HDFSBackedStateStore renames temporary files to delta files as it commits new versions. It however doesn&apos;t check whether the rename succeeded. If the rename fails, then recovery will not be possible. It should fail during the rename stage.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
